data.description: This home is a dream come true, ready for immediate move-in. Offering the convenience of one-story living, it features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a dedicated office, and an additional flexible space nestled between the secondary bedrooms. With a three-car garage and the added bonus of a pool, it's the epitome of comfort and luxury. Abundant natural light fills the space, accentuating the bright white kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, and subway tile backsplash. The living room boasts large windows and a cozy fireplace. The primary suite is generously proportioned and includes an ensuite with dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a walk-in glass shower. The secondary bedrooms are roomy and conveniently separated by a versatile flex space, perfect for a family room, playroom, or game room. The backyard is a true paradise with its stunning extended wooden deck and inviting pool. Don't miss your chance to experience this incredible home - come and see it for yourself!
